  <p>«Mine is the ring plus the skin, but I drew a bear on the skin. Because the bear is the healing animal in the forest. I put feathers around, four great blue heron feathers. The heron is the bird of spiritual healing. You do not put random things like "let's put marbles, and decorate it like a Christmas tree. "No, no! You have to go with something which means something.»</p>
